-- Rubenstein Says Emerging Markets to Get Higher Private Equity Investments
-- B y   A r i f   S h a r i f
-- 2010-10-19T07:19:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-19/rubenstein-says-emerging-markets-to-get-higher-private-equity-investments.html
David Rubenstein, co-founder of the
Carlyle Group, said emerging markets will get higher private
equity investments.  He said no emerging market can compete with China for
private equity deals, while Brazil and India will also attract
investments. Rubenstein was speaking in Abu Dhabi today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
